OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry
OL,6,Fovernight with lengthy clear spells,
OL,7,Fwhich will allow temperatures to fall,
OL,8,Fgiving the risk of a frost, mainly in
OL,9,Fprone rural spots. Some patchy mist
OL,10,Fand fog is likely to form, perhaps
OL,11,Fwith some coastal low cloud.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FAny early mist and fog soon
OL,14,Fclearing, but cloud towards the coast
OL,15,Fmay linger. Some brightness remains
OL,16,Flikely, with sunny spells inland, but
OL,17,Ffeeling cool with an easterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
